93
00:07:08,601 --> 00:07:11,436
- Go on, open your prize.
- OK.

94
00:07:14,274 --> 00:07:16,600
- Do you like it?
- It's beautiful.

95
00:07:16,735 --> 00:07:19,024
All right!

96
00:07:19,154 --> 00:07:22,488
I was so nervous. I didn't know.
I... I hope you like it.

97
00:07:22,866 --> 00:07:27,410
The guy I bought it from says even if
it looks like a snake, don't worry,

98
00:07:27,538 --> 00:07:29,910
cos it won't bite you.

99
00:07:31,500 --> 00:07:33,825
It's beautiful.

100
00:07:34,295 --> 00:07:36,453
You know what's amazing?

101
00:07:36,589 --> 00:07:40,918
