<i>we hope he's qualified to do so.</i>

126
00:09:28,494 --> 00:09:30,653
<i>- Hope?</i>
<i>- Well, I know he is,</i>

127
00:09:30,788 --> 00:09:33,872
<i>but I don't want to sound too confident.</i>

128
00:09:34,000 --> 00:09:38,994
<i>We would like an exhibition bout with</i>
<i>your famous champion, Rocky Balboa.</i>

129
00:09:39,130 --> 00:09:42,499
<i>You think he can fight</i>
<i>someone as seasoned as Balboa?</i>

130
00:09:42,633 --> 00:09:46,845
<i>There is no one who can match his</i>
<i>strength, endurance or aggressiveness.</i>

131
00:09:46,971 --> 00:09:49,213
<i>You make him sound indestructible.</i>

132
00:09:49,348 --> 00:09:51,140
<i>Yes, he is.</i>

133
00:09:51,267 --> 00:09:55,395
<i>Can this mammoth Russian,</i>
<i>nicknamed the Siberian Express,</i>

134
00:09:55,521 --> 00:09:58,606
<i>wreak havoc among</i>
<i>the professional heavyweight ranks?</i>

135
00:09:58,734 --> 00:10:01,900
<i>Whoever he fights first,</i>
<i>it'll be one hot ticket.</i>

136
00:10:02,029 --> 00:10:05,813
<i>We'll be right back with a check on</i>
<i>today's pro football sports scoreboard.</i>

137
00:10:07,075 --> 00:10:09,115
