his... freakish strength?

165
00:11:52,516 --> 00:11:55,850
Like your Popeye,
he ate his spinach every day.

166
00:11:58,981 --> 00:12:02,184
- Shall we have a demonstration?
- Please do.

167
00:12:02,693 --> 00:12:08,280
