00:50:35,465 --> 00:50:37,707
<i>~ It's a battle of wills ~</i>

655
00:50:37,843 --> 00:50:42,670
<i>~ In the heat of attack,</i>
<i>it's the passion that kills ~</i>

656
00:50:42,806 --> 00:50:47,302
<i>~ That victory is yours alone ~</i>

657
00:50:48,270 --> 00:50:50,677
<i>~ In the burning heart ~</i>

658
00:50:50,814 --> 00:50:53,020
<i>~ Just about to burst ~</i>

659
00:50:53,150 --> 00:50:57,859
<i>~ There's a quest for answers,</i>
<i>an unquenchable thirst ~</i>

660
00:50:57,988 --> 00:51:02,733
<i>~ In the darkest night, rising like a spire ~</i>

661
00:51:02,868 --> 00:51:07,743
<i>~ In the burning heart,</i>
<i>the unmistakable fire ~</i>

662
00:51:10,792 --> 00:51:13,200
Like you requested, yes?

663
00:51:13,337 --> 00:51:16,124
- You requested this dumb location?
- Yeah.

664
00:51:16,715 --> 00:51:20,049
Why? You plannin' to grow
reindeer or somethin'?

665
00:51:21,763 --> 00:51:27,433
- I just wanted to get away from things.
- The equipment you requested is in barn.

666
00:51:30,480 --> 00:51:33,434
- Who are they?
- They?

667
00:51:33,566 --> 00:51:36,353
They are assigned to you.

668
00:51:36,486 --> 00:51:39,155
Official chaperons, yes?

669
00:51:39,280 --> 00:51:41,569
Where you go, they go.

670
00:51:42,533 --> 00:51:44,859
Oh, I have a bad dream here.

671
00:51:45,787 --> 00:51:50,199
- Paul, it's OK.
- OK? This is below human standards.

672
00:51:50,333 --> 00:51:54,746
There's no antennas. You gotta
complain. We'll crack out here!

673
00:51:54,879 --> 00:51:58,213
You have everything
I have been instructed to provide.

674
00:51:58,341 --> 00:52:02,588
We are finished, yes? <i>Da svidaniya.</i>

675
00:52:12,563 --> 00:52:14,604
No sparrin'?

676
00:52:17,403 --> 00:52:20,522
I don't think I need it any more, Paulie.

677
00:52:20,656 --> 00:52:23,064
No sparrin', no TV, nothin'?

678
00:52:23,492 --> 00:52:26,612
How the heck is he supposed
to train around here?

679
00:52:27,204 --> 00:52:29,991
No TV. What about the Rose Bowl game?

680
00:52:30,332 --> 00:52:34,460
No room service, I bet.
I hope they got my comics here.

681
00:52:34,586 --> 00:52:37,078
What a depressing vacation.

682
00:52:44,513 --> 00:52:46,553
Goddamn!

683
00:52:50,269 --> 00:52:54,978
<i>All right, you Chipmunks.</i>
<i>Ready to sing your song?</i>

684
00:52:55,107 --> 00:52:59,057
<i>~ Christmas, Christmastime is here ~</i>

685
00:52:59,612 --> 00:53:04,108
<i>~ Time for toys and time for cheer ~</i>

686
00:53:04,241 --> 00:53:08,619
<i>~ We've been good, but we can't last... ~</i>

687
00:53:08,747 --> 00:53:11,416
Checkmate, friend.

688
00:53:25,013 --> 00:53:28,014
- Yeah?
- Hey, champ. Can I come up?

689
00:53:28,141 --> 00:53:30,181
Yeah, sure.

690
00:53:32,646 --> 00:53:34,804
- How you doin'?
- Pretty good.

691
00:53:34,940 --> 00:53:39,186
- Some kinda weather we're havin', huh?
- Yeah, it's pretty rough.

692
00:53:39,319 --> 00:53:41,988
But for what you gotta do, it's good.

693
00:53:43,615 --> 00:53:46,485
- Toughen you up.
- I guess so.

694
00:53:46,618 --> 00:53:51,196
I know you're gonna have to do almost
everything alone, but I'll be with you.

695
00:53:51,331 --> 00:53:53,370
Yeah, I know.

696
00:53:53,500 --> 00:53:56,501
Apollo was like my son.

697
00:53:56,628 --> 00:53:59,166
I raised him.

698
00:53:59,297 --> 00:54:01,872
And when he died... a part of me died.

699
00:54:04,053 --> 00:54:06,805
But now... <i>you're</i> the one.

700
00:54:06,931 --> 00:54:11,260
You're the one that's gonna keep
his spirit alive. You're the one...

701
00:54:11,394 --> 00:54:15,522
that's gonna make sure
that he didn't die for nothing.

702
00:54:15,648 --> 00:54:18,649
Now you're gonna have
to go through hell,

703
00:54:18,776 --> 00:54:21,943
worse than any nightmare
that you ever dreamed.

704
00:54:22,238 --> 00:54:27,196
But in the end...
I know you'll be the one standin'.

705
00:54:28,995 --> 00:54:31,034
I'll try.

706
00:54:34,083 --> 00:54:36,123
I'll try.

707
00:54:40,214 --> 00:54:42,254
You know what you gotta do.

708
00:54:44,343 --> 00:54:46,799
Do it.

709
00:54:47,221 --> 00:54:49,261
Do it!

710
00:54:54,604 --> 00:54:56,644
Thanks, Duke.

711
00:59:10,281 --> 00:59:12,736
I couldn't stay away any more.

712
00:59:16,245 --> 00:59:18,701
I missed you.

713
00:59:20,916 --> 00:59:23,586
I missed <i>you.</i>

714
00:59:24,295 --> 00:59:27,166
I'm with you, no matter what.

715
00:59:27,466 --> 00:59:29,505
No matter what?

716
00:59:32,137 --> 00:59:34,379
No matter what.

717
01:00:20,019 --> 01:00:24,313
<i>~ Silent darkness creeps into your soul ~</i>

718
01:00:26,859 --> 01:00:31,403
<i>~ And removes the light of self-control ~</i>

719
01:00:33,866 --> 01:00:38,528
<i>~ The cage that holds</i>
<i>you captive has no doors ~</i>

720
01:00:41,207 --> 01:00:44,327
<i>~ Burnin' with determination ~</i>

721
01:00:44,460 --> 01:00:47,130
<i>~ To even out the score ~</i>

722
01:00:47,880 --> 01:00:51,546
<i>~ Heart's on fire ~</i>

723
01:00:51,676 --> 01:00:55,211
<i>~ Strong desire ~</i>

724
01:00:55,346 --> 01:00:59,474
<i>~ Rages deep within ~</i>

725
01:01:02,103 --> 01:01:05,353
<i>~ Heart's on fire ~</i>

726
01:01:05,481 --> 01:01:10,606
<i>~ Fever's risin' high ~</i>

727
01:01:14,533 --> 01:01:16,989
<i>~ The moment of truth is here ~</i>

728
01:01:18,579 --> 01:01:20,618
<i>~ Oh! ~</i>

729
01:01:24,627 --> 01:01:27,462
No pain. No pain.

730
01:01:58,577 --> 01:02:01,744
<i>~ Heart's on fire ~</i>

731
01:02:01,872 --> 01:02:05,740
<i>~ Strong desire ~</i>

732
01:02:05,876 --> 01:02:10,089
<i>~ Rages deep within ~</i>

733
01:02:12,884 --> 01:02:15,505
<i>~ Fever's risin' ~</i>

734
01:02:16,012 --> 01:02:19,132
<i>~ Energisin' ~</i>

735
01:02:19,599 --> 01:02:23,597
<i>~ Fight until the end ~</i>

736
01:02:26,815 --> 01:02:29,934
<i>~ Heart's on fire ~</i>

737
01:02:30,068 --> 01:02:33,733
<i>~ Strong desire ~</i>

738
01:02:33,863 --> 01:02:38,276
<i>~ Rages deep within ~</i>

739
01:03:54,696 --> 01:03:58,361
Drago!

740
01:04:00,327 --> 01:04:03,660
Drago!

741
01:04:06,500 --> 01:04:11,126
Drago!

742
01:04:13,048 --> 01:04:15,965
Hello, and merry Christmas
from a very unusual place.

743
01:04:16,093 --> 01:04:20,304
We're in Moscow. I'm Barry Tompkins,
along with Al Bandiero,

744
01:04:20,430 --> 01:04:24,380
and this promises to be the most
watched event in boxing history.

745
01:04:24,518 --> 01:04:29,678
The Iron Horse from America, Rocky
Balboa, comes here to the Soviet Union...

746
01:04:31,149 --> 01:04:36,061
Ivan Drago: Since that tragedy in Las
Vegas and the death of Apollo Creed,

747
01:04:36,196 --> 01:04:39,316
he's been re-nicknamed
"Death from Above".

748
01:04:50,461 --> 01:04:53,131
Drago! Drago!

749
01:05:11,232 --> 01:05:15,479
The general secretary of the Soviet
and other members of the Politburo

750
01:05:15,611 --> 01:05:20,570
have now made their way to their seats
high above the ring here in Moscow.

751
01:05:25,872 --> 01:05:30,581
I know you're kinda busy, but I wanna
tell you some things I never told you.

752
01:05:30,710 --> 01:05:35,787
I know sometimes I act stupid and I say
stupid things, but you kept me around

753
01:05:35,923 --> 01:05:40,052
when other people would've said
"Drop that bum." You give me respect.

754
01:05:40,178 --> 01:05:44,046
It's hard for me to say these kinda
things because that ain't my way,

755
01:05:44,183 --> 01:05:49,557
but if I could unzip myself and step out
and be someone else, I'd wanna be you.

756
01:05:49,688 --> 01:05:51,728
You're all heart, Rock.

757
01:05:54,276 --> 01:05:56,483
Thanks, Paulie.

758
01:05:56,612 --> 01:05:58,770
Now blast this guy's teeth out!

759
01:05:59,990 --> 01:06:02,564
I'll try.

760
01:06:17,466 --> 01:06:22,093
One of the fighters is starting to make his
way through this crowd toward the ring.

761
01:06:22,221 --> 01:06:26,550
- Listen to this crowd!
- This borders on pure hatred.

762
01:06:26,684 --> 01:06:31,559
Rocky's face: Absolutely like stone,
a picture of concentration,

763
01:06:31,689 --> 01:06:34,855
and the booing crowd here does
not seem to bother him one bit.

764
01:06:34,984 --> 01:06:37,654
The champ has a look that
could burn through lead.

765
01:06:37,779 --> 01:06:41,563
It seems the booing crowd has
absolutely no effect on the man.

766
01:06:41,700 --> 01:06:43,776
His concentration is like stone.

767
01:06:43,910 --> 01:06:46,282
- That's my dad.
- We know.

768
01:06:46,413 --> 01:06:48,785
What do you think we are - nerds?

769
01:06:48,915 --> 01:06:51,869
Listen to this crowd. It sounds insane.

770
01:06:59,467 --> 01:07:03,382
And now the entrance
of the Russian national champion.

771
01:07:03,513 --> 01:07:08,009
Ivan Drago, a man with
an entire country in his corner.

772
01:08:00,655 --> 01:08:03,655
Look at the expression
on the face of Ivan Drago.

773
01:08:03,783 --> 01:08:06,949
He seems impervious
to this madness of the crowd.

774
01:08:07,078 --> 01:08:09,948
He's like a volcano just waiting to erupt.

775
01:08:10,081 --> 01:08:14,790
The Russian is cool
as he acknowledges his premier.

776
01:08:16,420 --> 01:08:20,584
I would like to point out again,
this is a non-sanctioned fight.

777
01:08:20,716 --> 01:08:26,222
This is not for the title. The American
Boxing Commission has not sanctioned it.

778
01:10:01,319 --> 01:10:03,525
Ladies and gentlemen...

779
01:10:11,496 --> 01:10:13,205
Rocky Balboa!

780
01:10:17,753 --> 01:10:22,913
It's unbelievable.
I have never seen such a hostile crowd.

781
01:10:31,642 --> 01:10:33,516
Ivan Drago!

782
01:10:43,988 --> 01:10:49,326
Roaring for their champion!
The two men are walking to the centre.

783
01:10:49,451 --> 01:10:52,488
It's an unbelievable sight to see.

784
01:10:52,621 --> 01:10:54,661
They're toe to toe.

785
01:10:54,790 --> 01:10:59,785
The Russian towers above the American.
It's a true case of David and Goliath here.

786
01:10:59,920 --> 01:11:03,788
It's unbelievable, the...
the condition of both men.

787
01:11:05,009 --> 01:11:07,335
I must break you.

788
01:11:13,685 --> 01:11:17,184
Remember what I said
about wanting to be you?

789
01:11:17,314 --> 01:11:19,353
Forget it.

790
01:11:20,317 --> 01:11:22,356
Thanks, Paul.

791
01:11:30,535 --> 01:11:34,200
Take it straight to him, and be
a rock for me, you understand?

792
01:11:34,331 --> 01:11:38,163
Be a rock for me! Be strong!
All right? Take it to him! No pain.

793
01:11:38,293 --> 01:11:41,744
- No pain. No pain.
- No pain. No pain. All right, Rock. Do it!

794
01:11:44,466 --> 01:11:47,835
There's the bell.
Rocky comes to the centre of the ring,

795
01:11:47,969 --> 01:11:51,919
like the Russian, way back
into Balboa's corner now.

796
01:11:56,436 --> 01:11:59,770
- Get outta there!
- Let's go, Rocky!

797
01:12:03,152 --> 01:12:08,194
Balboa gets out of the corner, and it is
Drago backing Rocky up with a jab.

798
01:12:08,324 --> 01:12:13,828
And Balboa is not staying on balance
because of the long jab of the Russian.

799
01:12:13,955 --> 01:12:16,243
Brace yourself! Brace yourself!

800
01:12:21,337 --> 01:12:23,792
Hands up!

801
01:12:24,715 --> 01:12:26,459
- Charge him!
- Now!

802
01:12:26,592 --> 01:12:29,510
He can't seem to touch the Russian.

803
01:12:29,637 --> 01:12:34,465
Rocky pounding away, and he's just hit
him with everything he's got.

804
01:12:34,600 --> 01:12:37,222
And Drago just smiled at him.

805
01:12:38,980 --> 01:12:42,313
- Keep choppin' away!
- Chop him down! Chop him down!

806
01:12:48,155 --> 01:12:50,825
Rocky Balboa is in serious trouble!

807
01:12:50,950 --> 01:12:54,071
They might have to stop this one
before somebody gets killed.

808
01:12:54,204 --> 01:12:57,371
Reach and grab him! Reach and grab him!

809
01:12:59,751 --> 01:13:03,452
Rocky woke the sleeping giant,
and now he's paying the price!

810
01:13:03,588 --> 01:13:07,882
A right hand from Drago sends Rocky
Balboa 15 feet across the ring,

811
01:13:08,010 --> 01:13:10,465
and the champ is down!

812
01:13:15,892 --> 01:13:18,348
Come on! Get up!

813
01:13:20,731 --> 01:13:22,854
Hands up! Hands up!

814
01:13:29,406 --> 01:13:34,910
Drago continuing to punish Rocky.
He will not let him out of that corner,

815
01:13:35,037 --> 01:13:39,615
and Rocky Balboa is just trying to
get through this first round.

816
01:13:44,129 --> 01:13:48,792
The Russian just threw Rocky Balboa
into his own corner like a rag doll.

817
01:13:48,926 --> 01:13:51,464
What a tough three minutes
for Rocky Balboa.

818
01:13:51,596 --> 01:13:54,632
He's not only fighting
an invincible opponent,

819
01:13:54,766 --> 01:13:57,221
he's also fighting a hostile crowd,

820
01:13:57,352 --> 01:14:01,729
and the Russian premier and
most of the Politburo looking on.

821
01:14:01,856 --> 01:14:05,307
- What's happenin' out there?
- He's winnin'.

822
01:14:06,527 --> 01:14:09,528
- I see three of him out there.
- Hit the one in the middle.

823
01:14:09,656 --> 01:14:12,740
- Right! Hit the one in the middle!
- Yeah.

824
01:14:12,867 --> 01:14:15,275
You're not doing as you're told.

825
01:14:15,745 --> 01:14:18,532
The American is small and weak...

826
01:14:18,873 --> 01:14:20,248
Weak.

827
01:14:20,375 --> 01:14:25,500
Take his heart. If you hurt him, you'll
take his heart. No pain! Keep workin'!

828
01:14:28,007 --> 01:14:30,759
Round two.
It's been a one-sided fight so far.

829
01:14:30,885 --> 01:14:34,753
It'll take more than luck
for Rocky to survive this round.

830
01:14:35,014 --> 01:14:37,221
Slip him a hook, Rock! Slip him a hook!

831
01:14:37,350 --> 01:14:42,428
Balboa trying to stay in the middle
of the ring against the big Russian.

832
01:14:44,984 --> 01:14:47,688
Do what you gotta do! Stay with him!

833
01:14:53,200 --> 01:14:56,735
For all intent,
Balboa should be all finished,

834
01:14:56,870 --> 01:14:59,575
but he's fighting back ferociously.

835
01:15:03,752 --> 01:15:05,792
Rocky!

836
01:15:06,839 --> 01:15:12,046
Balboa goes down again from
a right hand! Bounces right back up.

837
01:15:13,012 --> 01:15:15,253
He's gettin' killed out there!

838
01:15:18,559 --> 01:15:22,259
Rocky Balboa has taken
Ivan Drago's best punches so far.

839
01:15:22,396 --> 01:15:27,188
He's cut and he's bleeding,
but he's on his feet and he's on the run!

840
01:15:33,157 --> 01:15:35,945
- He's cut! He's cut!
- The Russian's cut!

841
01:15:36,077 --> 01:15:41,238
And it's a bad cut! And now it's
Rocky Balboa coming after Ivan Drago!

842
01:15:51,176 --> 01:15:52,884
Incredible! Get him!

843
01:15:57,807 --> 01:16:01,223
Drago wants to go on!
He grabs Balboa by the throat!

844
01:16:01,353 --> 01:16:05,646
Balboa picking up the Russian and throws
him to the ground like a wrestler.

845
01:16:05,774 --> 01:16:09,771
It's a gutter war!
No holds barred in Moscow!

846
01:16:09,903 --> 01:16:13,402
Rocky may be on the receiving end
so far, but he's here to fight.

847
01:16:13,531 --> 01:16:16,568
This is shaping up to be
a personal war, and right now

848
01:16:16,701 --> 01:16:19,453
it's anybody's boxing match.

849
01:16:20,872 --> 01:16:24,822
You're doin' good, Rocko.
I couldn't do better myself.

850
01:16:25,168 --> 01:16:26,366
How can you do this?

851
01:16:26,503 --> 01:16:28,412
He's nothing... soft!

852
01:16:28,546 --> 01:16:31,383
You got him hurt bad. Now he's worried.

853
01:16:31,509 --> 01:16:34,379
You cut him! You hurt him! You see?

854
01:16:34,512 --> 01:16:37,003
You see? He's not a machine. He's a man!

855
01:16:37,264 --> 01:16:39,222
He's not human...

856
01:16:40,893 --> 01:16:43,728
He's like a piece of iron.

857
01:16:44,689 --> 01:16:48,307
- You want it more than he does! No pain!
- No pain.

858
01:16:48,442 --> 01:16:51,396
- No pain.
- No pain. OK! Take it to him!

859
01:16:51,529 --> 01:16:53,237
Take it to him! Take it to him!

860
01:17:11,507 --> 01:17:12,918
Get up!

861
01:17:54,301 --> 01:17:57,634
And a big right hand by Rocky Balboa!

862
01:18:24,207 --> 01:18:27,077
You're doin' fine. You're doin' great.

863
01:19:31,942 --> 01:19:34,065
Come on!

864
01:19:40,909 --> 01:19:43,579
A few cheers now for Rocky Balboa!

865
01:19:43,704 --> 01:19:46,621
Suddenly Moscow is pro-Rocky!

866
01:19:58,761 --> 01:20:00,967
No pain. No pain.

867
01:20:25,872 --> 01:20:28,078
Al, this place is ready to explode.

868
01:20:28,208 --> 01:20:32,122
Lethal punch after punch.
Amazing willpower!

869
01:20:32,253 --> 01:20:37,793
And Rocky's determination is beginning
to win over what was a hostile crowd.

870
01:20:37,926 --> 01:20:39,206
This is incredible.

871
01:20:40,178 --> 01:20:43,013
- What round is it?
- 15. One more round.

872
01:20:43,139 --> 01:20:46,140
There's no stoppin' us now.
This is our round.

873
01:20:46,267 --> 01:20:48,937
Rocky! Rocky!

874
01:20:51,439 --> 01:20:53,930
No stoppin' now!
You start and you don't stop!

875
01:20:54,067 --> 01:20:58,314
All your strength! All your power!
All your love! Everythin' you've got!

876
01:20:59,740 --> 01:21:02,825
You trained this fool. He's a disgrace.

877
01:21:03,661 --> 01:21:05,903
Listen to them...

878
01:21:06,038 --> 01:21:09,288
Our people cheer for HIM! You idiot.

879
01:21:09,709 --> 01:21:10,751
WIN!

880
01:21:16,090 --> 01:21:18,129
<i>Nyet!</i>

881
01:21:19,051 --> 01:21:21,008
I fight to win!

882
01:21:21,846 --> 01:21:23,044
For me!

883
01:21:24,765 --> 01:21:26,473
For me!

884
01:21:28,019 --> 01:21:32,727
To win you gotta knock him out! Punch
and punch till you can't punch no more!

885
01:21:33,107 --> 01:21:37,436
- This is your whole life here!
- Yeah, knock him out, Rocko.

886
01:21:37,570 --> 01:21:39,609
Do it now! Now!

887
01:21:39,739 --> 01:21:45,029
